---
description: Build, format, and test verification before commits
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Before suggesting any commit:
1. Run `npm test` from the root to execute all workspace tests via Node's built-in test runner
2. Run `npm run format` to verify Prettier formatting passes
3. Do not suggest bypassing `.husky/pre-commit` (lint-staged) or `.husky/commit-msg` (commitlint)
4. If any step fails, fix the issue before proceeding to commit
